## Common Issues and Fixes

1. **Unclosed tags** - Ensure every opening tag has a closing tag
   - Wrong: `<p>text`
   - Right: `<p>text</p>`

2. **Self-closing tags** - Add space and slash
   - Wrong: `<br>`, `<hr>`, `<img src="...">`
   - Right: `<br />`, `<hr />`, `<img src="..." />`

3. **Unsupported CSS** - Replace with CSS 2.1 alternatives
   - Replace `display: flex` with tables or floats
   - Replace `gap` with margin/padding
   - Replace CSS variables with actual values

4. **Special characters** - Use entities
   - & → `&amp;`
   - < → `&lt;`
   - > → `&gt;`

5. **Missing declaration** - Document must start with:
   ```xml
   <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
   <!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
   ```

